00:31:00.820 --> 00:31:01.990
at nakaligtas kami

00:31:01.990 --> 00:31:04.030
lahat para sa paghihiganti sa Qi Kingdom.

00:31:04.340 --> 00:31:06.620
So ikaw ang pangalawa Yesha?

00:31:07.380 --> 00:31:08.230
Hindi, hindi ako.

00:31:08.580 --> 00:31:09.310
